attributes.title: WIZARD - Concat Emails 2
attributes.description: Concat Emails
attributes.code:
<?php 
/*  
 *  Welcome to ProcessMaker 4 Script Editor 
 *  To access Environment Variables use getenv("ENV_VAR_NAME") 
 *  To access Request Data use $data 
 *  To access Configuration Data use $config 
 *  To preview your script, click the Run button using the provided input and config data 
 *  Return an array and it will be merged with the processes data 
 *  Example API to retrieve user email by their ID $api->users()->getUserById(1)['email'] 
 *  API Documentation https://github.com/ProcessMaker/docker-executor-php/tree/master/docs/sdk 
 */

$poolUsers = $data["poolUsers"];
$registeredEmails = [];

foreach ($poolUsers as $userInfo) {
    if ($userInfo["email"] != "") {
        $registeredEmails[] = $userInfo["email"];
    }
}

$filteredEmails = array_unique($registeredEmails);

return [
    "registeredEmails" => implode(', ', $filteredEmails)
];

attributes.title: WIZARD - Execute Template Configuration 2
attributes.description: Execute
attributes.code:
<?php 
/*  
 *  Welcome to ProcessMaker 4 Script Editor 
 *  To access Environment Variables use getenv("ENV_VAR_NAME") 
 *  To access Request Data use $data 
 *  To access Configuration Data use $config 
 *  To preview your script, click the Run button using the provided input and config data 
 *  Return an array and it will be merged with the processes data 
 *  Example API to retrieve user email by their ID $api->users()->getUserById(1)['email'] 
 *  API Documentation https://github.com/ProcessMaker/docker-executor-php/tree/master/docs/sdk 
 */

/*Init Guzzle (use endpoint) and set options */
$guzzleClient = new \GuzzleHttp\Client(['base_uri'=> $_SERVER['HOST_URL'],'verify' => false]);
$guzzleOptions['headers']['Accept'] = 'application/json';
$guzzleOptions['headers']['Authorization'] = 'Bearer ' . getenv('API_TOKEN');

/*Get Guided Template Collection Id*/

$guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/collections/guided-template';

try {
    $guidedTemplateId = $guzzleClient->request('GET', $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
    $collectionId     = json_decode($guidedTemplateId->getBody()->getContents());
} catch (\Throwable $th) {
    return [
        'errorCode' => $th->getCode(),
        'errorMessage' => $th->getMessage()
    ];
}

/*Init and match data from process*/

//$collectionId  = $config['collectionId'];
$companyName   = $data['companyName'];
$poolUsers     = $data['poolUsers'];
$bamboo        = $data['bamboo'];
/*Init auxiliar variables*/
$i = 0;
$userIDs = [];

/*Iterate over poolUsers array object, it contains a set of user information*/
if($data['hr']=="no"){
    foreach ($poolUsers as $userInfo) {
        $userName = strtolower($userInfo['firstName']) . "." . strtolower($userInfo['lastName']);

        $guzzleApi = "/api/1.0/users?filter=" . urlencode($userName);

        try {
            $res = $guzzleClient->request('GET', $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
            $existingUserRes = json_decode($res->getBody(), true)["data"];
            $existingUserID = $existingUserRes[0]["id"];
        } catch (\Throwable $th) {
            return [
                'errorCode' => $th->getCode(),
                'errorMessage' => $th->getMessage()
            ];
        }

        if ($existingUserID) {
            $digits = 4;
            $randomPin = rand(pow(10, $digits-1), pow(10, $digits)-1);
        } else {
            $randomPin = "";
        }

        /*Init and match data from poolUsers*/
        $user['username']  = $userName . $randomPin;
        $user['email']     = $userInfo['email'];
        $user['firstname'] = $userInfo['firstName'];
        $user['lastname']  = $userInfo['lastName'];
        $user['password']  = "Pr0cessmaker";
        $user['phone']     = 0;
        $user['cell']      = 0;
        $user['status']    = "ACTIVE";
        $user['is_administrator'] = true; // temporary fix for permission issues

        /*Add options for Guzzle and default empty ID*/
        $guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/users';
        $guzzleOptions['json'] = $user;
        $newUserID = "0";

        /*Save user on PM*/
        try {
            $res = $guzzleClient->request('POST', $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
        } catch (\Throwable $th) {
            return [
                'errorCode' => $th->getCode(),
                'errorMessage' => $th->getMessage()
            ];
        }

        if ($res->getStatusCode() == 201) { // user created
            // Select user, select ID
            $newUser = json_decode($res->getBody(), true);
            $newUserID = $newUser['id'];
        }

        /*Add ID property to corresponding poolUser position*/
        $data['poolUsers'][$i]['id'] = $newUserID;
        $i++;
    }
}

/*Init and match data from process and edited*/
$recordInfo['companyName'] = $companyName;

$recordInfo['email_platform'] = $data['email_platform'];
if($recordInfo['email_platform'] != "skip"){
    if (isset( $data['gmail']))
        $recordInfo['gmail'] = $data['gmail'];
    if (isset( $data['office']))
        $recordInfo['office'] = $data['office'];
}


$recordInfo['hr_platform'] = $data['hr_platform'];
if($recordInfo['hr_platform']!="skip") {
    if (isset( $data['bamboo']))
        $recordInfo['bamboo'] = $data['bamboo'];
    if (isset( $data['workday']))
        $recordInfo['workday'] = $data['workday'];
    if (isset( $data['sap']))
        $recordInfo['sap'] = $data['sap'];
}
else
    $recordInfo['poolUsers'] = $data['poolUsers'];

$recordInfo['erp_platform'] = $data['erp_platform'];
if($recordInfo['erp_platform'] != "skip"){
    if (isset( $data['oracle']))
        $recordInfo['oracle'] = $data['oracle'];
    if (isset( $data['sage']))
        $recordInfo['sage'] = $data['sage'];
    if (isset( $data['dynamics']))
        $recordInfo['dynamics'] = $data['dynamics'];
    if (isset( $data['acumatica']))
        $recordInfo['acumatica'] = $data['acumatica'];
}

/*Add options for Guzzle process helper request id*/

$process_launchpad_id = $data['process_launchpad_id'];
$guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/processes/' . $process_launchpad_id;

// Get the helper process request ID stored in the process properties
$res = $guzzleClient->request("GET", $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
$process = json_decode($res->getBody(), true);

/* Add options for Guzzle request */
$guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/collections/' . $collectionId . '/records';

/* Check if helperProcessRequestId exists to update or create a new record */
if (isset( $process['properties']['helperProcessRequestId'])) {
//if (true) {
    $helperProcessRequestId = $process['properties']['helperProcessRequestId'];
    //$helperProcessRequestId = "423";
    $guzzleApi .= '?pmql=data.helperProcessRequestId%20=%20%22' . $helperProcessRequestId . '%22';
    
    try {
        $res = $guzzleClient->request('GET', $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
        $existingRecordRes = json_decode($res->getBody(), true)["data"];
        $existingRecordID = $existingRecordRes[0]["id"];
        $recordInfo['helperProcessRequestId'] = $helperProcessRequestId;

        /* Edit options for Guzzle request */
        $guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/collections/' . $collectionId . '/records/' . $existingRecordID; 
        $guzzleMethod = "PUT";
    } catch (\Throwable $th) {
        return [
            'errorCode' => $th->getCode(),
            'errorMessage' => $th->getMessage()
        ];
    }
} else {
    $recordInfo['helperProcessRequestId'] = $data["_request"]["id"];
    $guzzleMethod = "POST";
}

$guzzleOptions['json'] = $recordInfo;

/* Update or Save data on Collection */
try {
    $res = $guzzleClient->request($guzzleMethod, $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
} catch (\Throwable $th) {
    return [
        'errorCode' => $th->getCode(),
        'errorMessage' => $th->getMessage()
    ];
}

if ($res->getStatusCode() == 201 || $res->getStatusCode() == 204) { 
    return [
        "setupComplete" => "yes"
    ];
}
